(40, 'Meerlust Pinot Noir', 8157, 'Meerlust Pinot Noir is a delicate and aromatic red wine with flavors of ripe cherry, cranberry, and earthy notes. It has a silky texture and a vibrant acidity.', 2019, 'Stellenbosch', ' R35.00 ', 'data:image/jpeg;base64,', 8, 'Pinot Noir', 'Red', 'Grilled salmon'),
