(43, 'Meerlust Shiraz', 8157, 'Meerlust Shiraz is a rich and spicy red wine with intense flavors of black pepper, blackberry, and hints of violet. It has a smooth, velvety texture and a long, lingering finish.', 2017, 'Stellenbosch', ' R35.00 ', 'data:image/jpeg;base64,', 8, 'Shiraz', 'Red', 'Grilled lamb'),
