(46, 'Meerlust Rosé', 8157, 'Meerlust Rosé is a dry and fruity rosé wine with notes of strawberry, watermelon, and floral aromas. It is light-bodied and perfect for summer sipping.', 2020, 'Stellenbosch', ' R20.00 ', 'data:image/jpeg;base64,', 7, 'Rosé', 'Rosé', 'Grilled shrimp'),
