(48, 'Torres Gran Coronas', 8241, 'Torres Gran Coronas is a rich and full-bodied red wine with flavors of blackberry, plum, and vanilla. It has a velvety texture and a long, smooth finish.', 2016, 'Penedès', ' R25.00 ', 'https://www.torres.es/sites/default/files/2022-04/VardonKennett_725x480px.jpg', 8, 'Red Blend', 'Red', 'Lamb chops');
