(8157, 'Meerlust Estate', 'Meerlust Road', 'Stellenbosch', 'Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'Meerlust Estate is a historic wine estate located in Stellenbosch, Western Cape. Known for its exceptional wines and beautiful vineyards, Meerlust Estate offers visitors a memorable wine tasting experience. With a rich heritage and a commitment to producing premium wines, Meerlust Estate is a must-visit for wine enthusiasts.\r\n\r\nVisit https://www.meerlust.co.za/ for more information.', 'data:image/jpeg;base64,'),
(8215, 'Wine tasting and tour at Mitre’s Edge', 'R44 (Adam Tas Road)', 'Klapmuts', ' Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'Watch the master winemaker at work, take mental notes as Lola pours her love and expertise into creating the finest wines. The Mitre’s estate is well recognized in the area as the perfect place to learn about wine and cheese pairing. Lola and her team have created the perfect pairings, for visitors to indulge in. all their cheeses are locally produced, and careful consideration is given to the texture, saltiness, and acidity of the cheese when pairing. If you’re a dog lover, there’s a bonus. The family owns 6 friendly furry pets, which are sure to melt your heart while the wine and cheeses melt in your mouths. Stroll around the vineyards with these dogs at your tail, constantly trying to distract you from concentrtong on the winery. Use WineTourism.com’s easy booking platform to confirm your visit at Mitre’s Edge. Enjoy a guided wine tasting and tour today.\r\n\r\nVisit https://www.winetourism.com/experience/wine-tasting-tour-at-mitres-edge/ for more information.', 'https://www.winetourism.com/files/2021/08/mitres-edge-wine-tasting-300x200-300x300.webp?1672199666'),
(8220, 'Castello di Amorosa', 'Via San Marco, 11', 'Calistoga', 'Tuscany', 'Italy', 'Yes', 'Castello di Amorosa is a stunning winery in Tuscany, Italy, known for its medieval-style castle and exceptional wines.', 'https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/17/ba/fa/db/castello-di-amorosa-took.jpg?w=1200&h=-1&s=1'),
(8223, 'La Motte Wine Estate', 'R45 Main Road', 'Franschhoek', 'Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'La Motte Wine Estate is nestled in the picturesque Franschhoek Valley in the Western Cape. It is renowned for its award-winning wines and stunning natural surroundings. Visitors can enjoy wine tastings, cellar tours, and explore the estate\'s art museum. With its rich history and commitment to quality, La Motte Wine Estate is a top destination for wine lovers.\r\n\r\nVisit https://www.la-motte.com/ for more information.', 'data:image/jpeg;base64,'),
(8241, 'Bodegas Torres', 'Maset, 6', 'Vilafranca del Penedès', 'Barcelona', 'Spain', 'Yes', 'Bodegas Torres is a prestigious winery located in the Penedès region of Catalonia, Spain. It is known for its commitment to sustainable winemaking practices and produces a wide range of excellent wines.', 'https://www.torres.es/sites/default/files/2022-04/VardonKennett_725x480px.jpg'),
(8243, 'Wine Tasting at Holden Manz Wine Estate', '3 Green Valley Road', 'Franschhoek', ' Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'Experience exquisite wine and food pairings at Holden Manz Wine Estate. Сarefully selected dishes from the restaurant paired with their award-winning wines made many guests come back again for the best impressions of the tour. A famous cheese and meat platter, as well as fish cakes and other dishes, are available at the estate’s restaurant.\r\nYou will be tasting several of their best wines from Cabernet Sauvignon, Cabernet Franc, Merlot and Syrah. A lovely walk through nature surrounding the winery will relax and delight you. During your visit, taste through several wines grown in different vineyards while listening to their techniques of turning the grapes into liquid treasure. At the end of the day, guests who want to recuperate can get it at the 5-star guest house and in the estate’s day spa.\r\nBook a wonderful wine tasting and tour to Holden Manz Wine Estate from the comfort of your own home.\r\n\r\nVisit https://www.winetourism.com/experience/wine-tasting-at-holden-manz-wine-estate/ for more information.\r\n', 'https://www.winetourism.com/files/2021/06/holden-manz-wine-estate-property-1125x786-300x300.webp?1670937798'),
(8320, 'Bosman Family Vineyards', 'Bosman Family Vineyards, Lelienfontein, Hexberg Road', 'Wellington', 'Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'Bosman Family Vineyards is situated on the farm Lelienfontein in Wellington in the Western Cape, South Africa. The farm produces wines for the local and export market, and is home to one of the most influential vine nurseries in Africa.', 'https://bosmanwines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/BOSMAN_logo_sqr.png');
