(8345, 'Hamilton Russell Vineyards', 'Hemel-en-Aarde Valley', 'Hermanus', 'Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'Hamilton Russell Vineyards is a boutique winery located in the Hemel-en-Aarde Valley near Hermanus. It is known for producing exceptional cool-climate wines, particularly Chardonnay and Pinot Noir. Visitors can enjoy wine tastings and guided tours of the vineyards and cellar. With its commitment to quality and unique terroir, Hamilton Russell Vineyards is a must-visit for wine enthusiasts.\r\n\r\nVisit https://www.hamiltonrussellvineyards.com/ for more information.', 'data:image/jpeg;base64,'),
(8346, 'Wine Tasting at Boachkloof Wines', 'R320 Hemel-En-Aarde Valley, Newton Johnson Vineyards', 'Hermanus', ' Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'Wines from Boachkloof Wines have a unique distinct character; the kind you will have to taste to find out but one that you will instantly be able to tell apart.\r\nYou will be warmly greeted by the winemakers at their estate and get to know a little bit of the family history of the Borman family. Rejoice in their red wines and white wines.\r\nYou and your family and your friends will have an amazing time at Boachkloof Wines.\r\n \r\nVisit https://www.winetourism.com/experience/wine-tasting-at-boachkloof-wines/ for more information.', 'https://www.winetourism.com/files/2021/07/boachkloof-wines-wine-bottle-592x382-300x300.webp?1673901142'),
(8354, 'Alvi\'s Drift Winery', 'Alvi’s Drift Private Cellar, Alfalfa Farm, Scherpenheuwel Road, Worcester, 6850', ' Cape Town', 'Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'Alvi\'s Drift winery is an award-winning South African private wine cellar in the Worcester wine region in SA\'s Breede River Valley.', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0608/0505/4720/files/Alvi_s-Drift-Logo-Blue.png?v=1645089435'),
(8412, 'Newton Johnson Family Vineyards', 'Hemel-en-Aarde Valley', 'Hermanus', 'Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'Newton Johnson Family Vineyards is a family-owned winery situated in the Hemel-en-Aarde Valley near Hermanus. It specializes in producing premium cool-climate wines, including Chardonnay, Pinot Noir, and Syrah. Visitors can enjoy wine tastings, cellar tours, and breathtaking views of the vineyards. With its dedication to sustainable practices and artisanal winemaking, Newton Johnson Family Vineyards offers a unique wine experience.\r\n\r\nVisit https://www.newtonjohnson.com/ for more information.', 'data:image/jpeg;base64,'),
(8420, 'Château Margaux', '1, Margaux', 'Bordeaux', 'Gironde', 'France', 'Yes', 'Château Margaux is a prestigious winery located in the Bordeaux region of France, famous for producing some of the finest red wines in the world.', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/07/Margaux_exterior.jpg/450px-Margaux_exterior.jpg'),
(8569, 'Robertson Winery', '160 Voortrekker Road', 'Robertson', 'Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'Robertson Winery is a renowned wine producer located in Robertson, Western Cape. It is known for its wide range of high-quality wines, including Chenin Blanc, Shiraz, and Cabernet Sauvignon. Visitors can enjoy wine tastings, cellar tours, and delicious food pairings. With its rich winemaking heritage and commitment to excellence, Robertson Winery offers an unforgettable wine experience.\r\n\r\nVisit https://www.robertsonwinery.co.za/ for more information.', 'https://wetu.com/ImageHandler/h1160x432/18061/Van%20loveren%201.jpg'),
(8642, 'Visiting and Tasting at the Newton Johnson Family Vineyards', 'Polkadraai Road', 'Stellenbosch', ' Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'At the Newton Johnson Family Vineyards, vineyard tours are offered to guests who would like to explore the estate’s vast vineyards. The tour takes guests into the vineyards to learn more about practices such as vine training and the sustainble practices that are employed on the farm. The vineyards where one walks through are located at an altitide of 300m above sea level, providing wonderful panoramic views of the valley, the mountains and the ocean. This is the perfect experience for those looking to learn more about how the Newton Johnson Family Vineyards wines are produced before relaxing and enjoying a drink at the tasting room.\r\n\r\nVisit https://www.winetourism.com/experience/visiting-and-tasting-at-the-newton-johnson-family-vineyards/ for more information.', 'https://www.winetourism.com/files/2023/02/newton_johnson_family_vineyards_jn-1500x500.webp'),
(8643, 'Penfolds Magill Estate', '78 Penfold Road', 'Magill', 'South Australia', 'Australia', 'Yes', 'Penfolds Magill Estate is an iconic winery in South Australia, famous for its historic vineyards and high-quality wines, including the renowned Penfolds Grange.', 'https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/4e/7a/a2/over-170-years-of-winemaking.jpg?w=900&h=600&s=1'),
(8765, 'Robert Mondavi Winery', '7801 St Helena Hwy', 'Oakville', 'California', 'United States', 'Yes', 'Robert Mondavi Winery is a renowned winery situated in the heart of Napa Valley, California. It is known for its exquisite wines and picturesque vineyards.', 'https://www.sthelena.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Robert-Mondavi.png'),
(8821, 'Nederburg Wines', 'Sonstraal Road', 'Paarl', 'Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'Nederburg Wines is a prestigious wine estate located in Paarl, Western Cape. It is renowned for its award-winning wines and rich winemaking heritage. Visitors can enjoy wine tastings, cellar tours, and explore the estate\'s beautiful gardens. With its commitment to quality and innovation, Nederburg Wines offers a remarkable wine experience.\r\n\r\nVisit https://www.nederburg.com/ for more information.', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRG2Y-9bs6-lEyJadF6KyaQg4AcPXLNbHyoRg&usqp=CAU'),
(9015, 'McGregor Winery', 'Voortrekker Street', 'McGregor', 'Western Cape', 'South Africa', 'Yes', 'McGregor Winery is a boutique winery located in the picturesque town of McGregor, Western Cape. It is known for its small-batch, handcrafted wines made from locally grown grapes. Visitors can enjoy wine tastings, cellar tours, and soak in the peaceful atmosphere of the estate. With its intimate setting and passion for quality winemaking, McGregor Winery offers a delightful wine experience.\r\n\r\nVisit https://www.mcgregorwinery.co.za/ for more information.', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQlkeY0rZAPWZcTxkC9WJ00MXs_qiS9eg3h2g&usqp=CAU');
